Dependencies
------------

To build the example and test executables, CMake is required.

* CMake: http://www.cmake.org

Installing
----------

Using CMake:

  $ tar zxvf smiley-x.y.tar.gz
  $ cd smiley-x.y
  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ cmake ..
  $ make
  $ make test           [optional]
  $ make install

Without CMake:

  Copy the smiley.h header file to a location that is in the include path for
  the application you are building.
